### Animal Zoo Report Service - API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

###############################################################################
# REPORT ENDPOINTS
###############################################################################

### 1. Get Daily Feeding Report (Today)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/daily-feeding
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 2. Get Daily Feeding Report (Specific Date - 2025-10-20)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/daily-feeding?date=2025-10-20
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 3. Get Daily Feeding Report (Specific Date - 2025-10-15)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/daily-feeding?date=2025-10-15
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 4. Get Animal Health Check Report (Last 7 days - default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/animal-health-check
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 5. Get Animal Health Check Report (Specific Date Range)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/animal-health-check?fromDate=2025-10-01&toDate=2025-10-20
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 6. Get Animal Health Check Report (Last 30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/animal-health-check?fromDate=2025-09-20&toDate=2025-10-20
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 7. Get Animal Health Check Report (Specific Week)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/animal-health-check?fromDate=2025-10-14&toDate=2025-10-21
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 8. Get Animal Health Check Report (Single Day)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/animal-health-check?fromDate=2025-10-20&toDate=2025-10-20
Accept: {{contentType}}

###############################################################################
# TEST EDGE CASES
###############################################################################

### 9. Get Daily Feeding Report (No Date Parameter - Should use today)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/daily-feeding
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 10. Get Health Check (Only fromDate - Should use current time as toDate)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/animal-health-check?fromDate=2025-10-01
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 11. Get Health Check (Only toDate - Should use 7 days before as fromDate)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/animal-health-check?toDate=2025-10-20
Accept: {{contentType}}

###############################################################################
# HEALTH CHECK
###############################################################################

### 12. Application Health Check (if actuator is enabled)
# GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health
# Accept: {{contentType}}

